title: Cisco Meraki: Appliance Uplinks
agents: cisco_meraki
catalog: os/services
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check plug-in monitors appliance uplinks.

 In order to make this check plug-in work, you have to configure the ruleset for
 the special agent {{Cisco Meraki}} to include the "Appliance uplink statuses"
 section.

 The check plug-in itself can be configured via the corresponding rule
 {{Cisco Meraki appliance uplinks}}.

discovery:
 One service per organisation ID is created.
